{"tid":2449042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721白衣人︱周天行確定不會傳召任何警員出庭作供","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T12:22:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6fedad1408c445c12247f75cad6e65cbaf35764d","tid":2449042,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"元朗721白衣人涉暴動案，審訊進入第17天。控方今表示毋須傳召剪片及辨認被告的兩名警員出庭，改以書面方式呈遞口供，現餘下只剩一名證人的證供，就可完結控方案情，控方不會傳召任何警員證人，確認本案為「無警審訊」。惟早前多名證人均供稱，有警員曾在現場出現。<br />\n<br />\n此外，證人N及O日前均供稱，曾在近J出口的元朗站大堂，目擊有市民指罵到場警員，怒斥他們姍姍來遲。N和O亦同樣看見有警員抵達西鐵站廁所，其後護送傷者離開。N其後收到朋友通知，指警員到場後又離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/TEGWE4LDGRFG3GDKBVTXODWAYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FTEGWE4LDGRFG3GDKBVTXODWAYU%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=35493a62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FTEGWE4LDGRFG3GDKBVTXODWAYU%2F&h=543f1ab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/TEGWE4LDGRFG3GDKBVTXODWAYU/</a>"},{"pid":"6fa0e8082252dfcc53ee3ff24045ded6082e7df9","tid":2449042,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a92e9610d1de1c1222f8edd6737f8aa50246c9","tid":2449042,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk